      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example benefits from critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with a functional M-Variable differential lock and crisp steering rack feedback. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust, delivering a linear power curve and an unmistakable 8,000 RPM redline soundtrack.",
