      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This premium sedan offers a refined driving experience, blending sophisticated styling with dependable performance. The exterior presents beautifully in a metallic finish that still catches the light, though a close inspection reveals a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical of highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the leather seating is well-preserved with only light creasing on the driver's bolster, and the wood trim remains vibrant. All tech features, from the navigation system to the heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced at regular intervals, ensuring the car drives with the same precision it did years ago. It is a solid, honest vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of reliable service.",
      "price": 34850.0,
