    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with a lot of love? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in great shape! It runs super smooth, looks sharp on the road, and is ready for its next adventure. Whether you need a dependable commuter or something for weekend road trips, this one is a fantastic find. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love it!",
