    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This unit remains mechanically robust with a recently serviced VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, delivering power through a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Riding on a well-sorted suspension with fresh bushings and original dampers, the turn-in remains sharp. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance engineering.",
